criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. diagnosis of a functional psychotic disorder (schizophrenia-related disorder OR
             bipolar disorder or major depressive disorder with the presence of a severe episode
             with psychotic features within the past 2 years);

          2. sufficient fluency in English to make use of the resources;

          3. overall intellectual functioning within normal limits (WTAR estimated IQ>70);

        Exclusion criteria (e) change in medication or in-patient admission in the previous 2
        months;
